      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Society for the Advancement of all Natural Sciences of Marburg. ¶ To Baron Ferdinand von Muller ¶ Melbourne ¶  ¶ In the name and on instructions of the Society for the Advancement of all Natural Scien...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">96.08.00a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Otto von Heusinger</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Document bound in with an incomplete set of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Sitzungsberichte der Gesellschaft zur Beförderung der gesammten Naturwissenschaften zu Marburg</seg> for 1895.</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Gesellschaft zur Beförderung der gesammten Naturwissenschaften in Marburg.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">An Herrn Baron Ferdinand von Müller.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Im Namen und Auftrage der Gesellschaft zur Beförderung der gesammten Naturwissenschaften zu Marburg habe ich die Ehre:</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">Sitzungsberichte 1894 und 1895</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">zu übersenden.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Ich bestätige zugleich mit bestem Danke den Empfang</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="de">siehe Sitzungsberichte</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">und bitte um Fortdauer des wissenschaftlichen Verkehrs.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Mit vorzüglicher Hochachtung</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Der Sekretär</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Heusinger</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text"
                    style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, 'Times New Roman'; ">Marburg,</seg> August 1896</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">Society for the Advancement of all Natural Sciences of Marburg.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">To Baron Ferdinand von Muller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In the name and on instructions of the Society for the Advancement of all Natural Sciences of Marburg I have the honour to send you</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Sitzungsberichte</seg> 1894 and 1895.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">At the same time I acknowledge receipt with best thanks</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">see <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Sittzungsberichte</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Receipt of M's 'second systematic census' (B89.12.03) was acknowledged in the 1896 volume of the Society's <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Sitzungsberichte</seg>, no. 2, February 1896, p. 33.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">and request continuation of scientific contact.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With special respect</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Secretary</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Heusinger</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Marburg, August 1896</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
